## Kubernetes Deployment

### Raw Manifests

The Kubernetes manifests automatically deploy the tracing backend:

```bash
# Apply all manifests (includes tracing)
./k8s/kubectl-apply.sh apply
```

### Helm Charts

The Helm chart includes the tracing backend as a configurable component:

```bash
# Install with tracing enabled (default when generated)
helm install <%= baseName.toLowerCase() %> ./helm/<%= baseName.toLowerCase() %>

<%_ if (distributedTracingZipkin) { _%>
# Disable Zipkin
helm install <%= baseName.toLowerCase() %> ./helm/<%= baseName.toLowerCase() %> --set zipkin.enabled=false
<%_ } else if (distributedTracingJaeger) { _%>
# Disable Jaeger
helm install <%= baseName.toLowerCase() %> ./helm/<%= baseName.toLowerCase() %> --set jaeger.enabled=false
<%_ } _%>
```
